{"tid":1802371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1.1 問下自己良心 有咩藉口唔出","createTime":"2019-12-29T11:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T01:28:37.000Z","uid":200274,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfd707215e2ec41bc278d387690ccf1d20ea39f","tid":1802371,"uid":200274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:57:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NAS7AzV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNAS7AzV.png&h=0f125f6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.1 見</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e2400848b88af36f0607e8e5002cc4ec19d7bc8b","tid":1802371,"uid":47020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:58:11.000Z","msg":"遲到好過冇到啊各位"},{"pid":"2322351c48bd87a64ad7af49aa43564df2d50a4c","tid":1802371,"uid":200274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:00:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">半年喇 <br />\n唔好再淨係坐喺屋企po文宣喇<br />\n唔夠㗎<br />\n求下你哋出嚟啦</span></strong>"},{"pid":"2edf09808fd597d26805a290cd11503eb40c5bd6","tid":1802371,"uid":116054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:00:48.000Z","msg":"致所有懷獨立意志的香港人：<br />\n<br />\n我們嚮往自由，我值得擁有民主。但坐權力椅子上的是一群冷血無恥，將年青人置於死地的獨裁者。面對酷刑、殘殺、強姦，我們不能視若無睹。香港民族必須盡快建構獨立意志，在中共未來不穩局勢下尋求獨立出路，這樣才能對得起我們的下一代。假若我們再次錯失時代革命，我們便再沒有機會談香港的命途，只因我們全都在集中營相見。<br />\n<br />\n選舉完了，人權民主法過了，我們沒有再修飾的藉口。為了受了傷害的人，為了仍然被困的手足，我們不能再害怕。請各支持獨立意志的香港人在元旦日一起加入我們的旗隊，讓獨立的民意展現出來，重燃對香港命途的希望。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/buBgtWy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbuBgtWy.png&h=1d7211e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"775ba06a66855aa8f51ac9f741044bd569e6bb42","tid":1802371,"uid":151256,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:01:19.000Z","msg":"12月8出完咪又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4577c524f3b77ba6b17601f7b46dbb8f1de046e8","tid":1802371,"uid":20027