7271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:17:16.000Z","msg":"塞爆港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fd373ab28fd0e1f93360209e28ba7ad3c04d8d","tid":1802371,"uid":178660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:17:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"482fbd01d35586ab2b8355847e2de09acdfb2350","tid":1802371,"uid":334232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddfd707215e2ec41bc278d387690ccf1d20ea39f","tid":1802371,"uid":200274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:57:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NAS7AzV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNAS7AzV.png&h=0f125f6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.1 見</span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"🖐🏻🖕🏻"},{"pid":"c1bcdb1acb9c031588700fb664ce5b5bd3fa66a4","tid":1802371,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:19:16.000Z","msg":"<code>當權者不可能讓步答應五大訴求，呢個唔係林鄭政府尊嚴嘅問題，而係因為實行五大訴求與摧毀政權穩定性無異。</code><br />\n<br />\n<code>1. 徹查警暴，此舉減低武裝力量（警察）對政府嘅忠誠 ；</code><br />\n<br />\n<code>2. 撤回暴動定性及撤銷控罪，等同承認過去幾月嘅抗爭係正義而有效；</code><br />\n<br />\n<code>3. 成立獨立調查委員會，等同承認政權無法自行執行公正嘅調查；</code><br />\n<br />\n<code>4. 以行政命令解散立法會並實行雙普選，等同摧毀現今政府嘅「合法」基礎。</code><br />\n<br />\n<code>對當權者而言，回應訴求等同要特區政府自我毀滅，故此政權係冇可能主動滿足訴求。</code>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"fc5e263cc02601415038dd8e85fd0870ac1a43a5","tid":1802371,"uid":200274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:22:44.000Z","msg":"【元旦大遊行 不反已出】<br />\n<br />\n民陣已收到警方發出的不反對通知書，<br />\n可以正式同各位講多次，1.1 維園見！<br />\n<br />\n元旦遊行當日，將會有超過 40 個新成立工會同大家見面，歡迎大家了解詳情，加入你所屬行業的工會，壯大抗爭的組織力量。<br />\n<br />\n毋忘承諾，並肩同行，<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可，<br />\n一月一，維園見！<br />\n<br />\n2020.1.1 星期三 Wednesday｜2PM<br />\n維園中央草坪 遊行至 遮打道行人專用區<br />\nFrom Victoria Park (Central Lawn) to <br />\nChater Road Pedestrian Precinct<br />\n<br />\n*已取得不反對通知書<br />\n*Letter of No Objection Received<br />\n<br />\n【海報、單張下載】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2QwFg31\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QwFg31&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK95mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=42c1617d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2QwFg31</a>"}}